He will appear at Boston Magistrates' Court on January 8, next year.

The theft occurred between 6pm on Tuesday, December 10 and 6.40am the following morning.

Among the stolen items were 260 oven-ready partridges, 400 kilos of venison and 2,000 feathered pheasants.

A quarter tank of diesel was also taken.

